6.6.5 Dash Board / Visualization/ Reports of the Forecasts:
114
Tender Document SAMAST KERALA
The forecasting shall be delivered with the help of proper visualization / Dash boards /
Reports, which can be accessed by KSEBL engineers through log in provisions. Dashboard /
Visualization/ Reports shall have provisions for query-based sorting / filter options including
 historical forecast / trends, the minute details of which shall be finalized with the supplier
after discussions. The Dashboard shall also have the provisions of error reporting between
the forecasted value and actual value, and also possible reasons for the anomaly
(Tripping /unforeseen weather conditions) so that contractor can correct forecast in future.
Desired deliverables from the forecast module are detailed in Annexure 1.